@refreshToken=

### 어드민 로그인
# @name adminLogin
POST {{baseUrl}}/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "admin@codeit.com",
  "password": "AdminPass123!"
}

### 차량 등록
POST {{baseUrl}}/cars
Authorization: bearer {{accessToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
	"carNumber": "12가1234",
	"manufacturer": "기아",
	"model": "K3",
	"manufacturingYear": 2023,
	"mileage": 30,
	"price": 1000000,
	"accidentCount": 1,
	"explanation": "설명",
	"accidentDetails": "사고설명"
}

### 차량 목록 조회 (페이지네이션 + 검색)
# - `page` : number (현재 페이지 번호)
# - `pageSize` : number (페이지당 아이템 수)
# - `status`: possession | contractProceeding | contractCompleted (차량 상태)
# - `searchBy` : carNumber | model (검색 기준)
# - `keyword` : string (검색어)
GET {{baseUrl}}/cars?page=1&pageSize=1&status=possession&searchBy=model&keyword=K3
Authorization: bearer {{accessToken}}
Content-Type : application/json

### 차량 목록 조회
GET {{baseUrl}}/cars
Authorization: bearer {{accessToken}}
Content-Type : application/json

### 차량 상세 정보 조회
GET {{baseUrl}}/cars/1
Authorization: bearer {{accessToken}}
Content-Type : application/json

### 차량 수정
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/cars/1
Authorization: bearer {{accessToken}}
Content-Type : application/json

{
  "carNumber": "99가1234",
	"manufacturer": "현대",
	"model": "그랜저",
	"manufacturingYear": 2020,
	"mileage": 30,
	"price": 1000000,
	"accidentCount": 1,
	"explanation": "string",
	"accidentDetails": "string"
}

### 차량 삭제
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/cars/1
Authorization: bearer {{accessToken}}
Content-Type : application/json

### 차량 모델 목록 조회
GET {{baseUrl}}/cars/models
Authorization: bearer {{accessToken}}
Content-Type : application/json

